node.text:
Cream soda or beer? You decide. 4pks drop at 12pm at both locations today. This beer will also be on tap today in Ridgewood! Check out all the new releases info below:

YOUR DAD’S RETRO FASHIONED CREAM SODA
Soda-Sour Ale / 6% / Retro flavors of sweet cream, vanilla ice cream, and soda syrup! Semi-sweet, effervescent, nostalgic. Contains milk sugar.
$18/4pk

NO, I DON’T WANT TO GO TO SPACE - I JUST WANT TO GO TO SPAIN.
Pale Ale / 5.3% / Double dry-hopped with Motueka and Nelson. Clean, refreshing, dank.
$15/4pk

EVIL WATER - HAWAIIAN PUNCH
Imperial Hard Seltzer / 7.4% / Big punch flavors of cherry, raspberry, mango, pineapple, and passion fruit. Semi-dry, fruity, effervescent.
$14/4pk

EVIL WATER - RACE DAY
Runners Seltzer / 4.5% / The perfect runner’s seltzer with juiced up notes of pineapple, aloe, and electrolytes.  Light, crispy, thirst-quenching.
$14/4pk

node.text:
⚡️IMPORTANT TAPROOM UPDATES⚡️

Ridgewood, Queens:
To comply with the “Key to NYC” mandate, all guests must show proof of vaccination (physical card with ID or excelsior pass with ID) to sit inside the greenhouse. Guests who are not vaccinated must sit outside and wear a mask when inside the greenhouse for any reason.

DUMBO, Brooklyn:
This location will go back to operating as a vaccination-only taproom. All guests must show proof of vaccination to sit inside the taproom. The to-go window will continue to serve to-go coffee, draft beers, as well as 4pks and crowlers.

We thank you all for your patience while we navigate these ever-changing mandates and protocols. Stay safe NY🗽

The perfect breakfast beer was just tapped in Ridgewood! Come try it out, we’re slinging beers ‘til 10pm here and 11pm in DUMBO.

CONTINENTAL BREAKFAST SOUR BLACKBERRY YOGHURT VERSION
Breakfast Sour Ale / 7.5% / Robust notes of Ethiopian coffee, juicy blackberries, and breakfast yoghurt. Sweet, roasty, smoothie-like.

The perfect brunch seltzer is now available in 4pks at both taprooms! Be sure to grab a pack for tomorrow’s Sunday brunch 🍊🥂 And don’t forget to check out the @evilwaternyc pop-up happening this weekend in Ridgewood! Taproom hours in bio.

EVIL WATER PASTRY SELTZER - VANILLA MIMOSA
Craft Hard Seltzer / 5% / The perfect balance of fresh-squeezed OJ, delicate vanilla bean, and Chardonnay must. Juicy, effervescent, semi-sweet.

node.text: The first @tracksmithrunning x @eviltwinbrewingnyc meet has kicked off this morning! They will be hosting long runs every Saturday morning starting at 8am. Bag drop & pre-run coffee from @seycoffee starts at ETNYC Dumbo, heading into Manhattan with pacing groups, water stops, and delicious beers once finished. All runners are welcome as the route is easy to extend or shorten. Find more details at the link in our bio!

node.text: We love “wfh” at the DUMBO taproom during early morning hours ☕️ Each table has plug-in available, plus coffee and pastries are served ‘til 2pm! Beer starts at noon, so be sure to stay for a lager or two 😉
